---
title: Indian Haloumi & Roast Veggie Curry with Garlic Rice & Flaked Almonds
description: This darkly rich haloumi curry is like a golden sunset. Filled to the brim with bright veggies and a sprinkling of flair from the toasted almonds, we reckon this beaming bowl will add the spice you never knew you needed to your night.
